1.List product name, price except soap on price order.
mysql> SELECT * FROM PRODUCT;
+------+---------------+-------+
| P_ID | P_NAME        | PRICE |
+------+---------------+-------+
|  117 | Book          |   184 |
|  222 | Floor cleaner |   326 |
|  230 | Bottle        |   255 |
|  457 | Bag           |  1020 |
|  786 | Snacks        |   551 |
|  880 | Soap          |    82 |
|  986 | Lunch Box     |   408 |
+------+---------------+-------+
7 rows in set (0.01 sec)

mysql> select P_NAME,PRICE from PRODUCT where P_NAME!='Soap' order by PRICE asc; 
